import React,{useState} from 'react' import Plus from '../Assets/images/Plus.svg' const Inputarea = () => { const [designer,setDesigner]= useState(0); const[frontEnd,setFrontEnd]= useState(0); const[backEnd,setBackEnd]= useState(0); const[qa,setQA]= useState(0); return (
Designer
setDesigner(designer+1)} src={Plus}/> {designer}
Front End Developer
setFrontEnd(frontEnd+1)}src={Plus}/> {frontEnd}
Back End Developer
setBackEnd(backEnd+1)}src={Plus}/> {backEnd}
QA
setQA(qa+1)}src={Plus}/> {qa}
) } export default Inputarea;
